@using BookApp.Web.Models.Common.Modals
@using BookApp.Web.Models.Student
@using BookApp.Web.Startup
@using BookApp.Web.Host.Controllers
@model CreateStudentViewModel
@{
    ViewBag.Title = L("Student");
    ViewBag.CurrentPageName = PageNames.Student;
}
@section scripts{
    <environment names="Development">
        <script src="~/view-resources/Views/Student/Create.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
    </environment>
}

    <body>
        <div class="bg-opacity-5 py-2" id="form">
            <form style="text-align: center" name="StudentInformationForm" role="form" class="form-validation form-horizontal">
                <div class="container">
                    <h3 class="col-md-10">Student Information Form</h3><br>
                </div>
                <input type="hidden" name="Id" value="@Model?.Id" class="form-control">
                <div class="col-md-9 mb-10">
                    <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane container active">
                        <div class="form-group row required" style="text-align: center">
                            <label class="col-md-3 col-form-label">Name</label><br>
                            <div class="col-md-9">
                                <input type="text" name="StudentName" id="StudentName" value="@Model?.StudentName" class="form-control" placeholder="Full Name" required maxlength="255" minlength="2">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group row required" style="text-align: center">
                            <label class="col-md-3 col-form-label">Contact Number</label><br>
                            <div class="col-md-9">
                                <input type="tel" name="StudentContactNumber" id="StudentContactNumber" value="@Model?.StudentContactNumber" class="form-control" placeholder="Contact Number" required maxlength="32" minlength="2">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group row required text-align: center">
                            <label class="col-md-3 col-form-label">Email</label><br>
                            <div class="col-md-9">
                                <input type="email" name="StudentEmail" id="StudentEmail" value="@Model?.StudentEmail" class="form-control" placeholder="Email" required maxlength="255" minlength="2">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group row required text-align: center">
                            <label class="col-md-3 col-form-label">Department</label><br>
                            <div class="col-md-9">
                                <input type="text" name="StudentDepartment" id="StudentDepartment" value="@Model?.StudentDepartment" class="form-control" placeholder="Department" required maxlength="255" minlength="2">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row modal-footer justify-content-between">
                    <button type="button" class="back-button btn btn-default" name="Back">Back</button>
                    <button type="submit" class="save-button btn btn-primary" name="Create">Save</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </body>


